title: Overcoming Past Sexual Trauma
itunes:author: Guests: Dr. Cliff & Joyce Penner
itunes:summary: If you or your spouse have experienced sexual abuse, you are not alone. With God's help, your healing process can begin today. Greg, Erin and John offer hope to women who've been sexually abused. Receive the book Enjoy! with your gift of any amount!
